BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20260331T230000Z
DTEND:20260401T000000Z
LOCATION:AUDITORIUM
GEO:39.168443;-86.517858
SUMMARY:Daniel Tosh: My First Farewell Tour
DESCRIPTION:Comedian\, host\, writer\, and producer Daniel Tosh is coming
  to Bloomington as part of his My First Farewell Tour arriving this sprin
 g. Tickets go on sale Friday\, November 21 at 10 a.m. ET.  Daniel is wide
 ly known for hosting and creating TOSH.0 on Comedy Central. The show show
 cased internet clips with the addition of Daniel's comedic perspective an
 d was one of the longest-running comedy series for Comedy Central.  He ca
 n currently be heard and seen hosting his video podcast\, TOSH SHOW. The 
 show premiered garnering millions of watches and listens in the first wee
 ks.  Daniel has performed live stand-up comedy to sold out venues all ove
 r the world including New Zealand\, Australia\, Montreal\, and Ireland. F
 ollowing his 2025 US Daniel Tosh Live tour\, he just announced his new 20
 26 North America stand-up tour\, Daniel Tosh:My First Farewell Tour.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Comedian\, host\, writer\, and producer
  Daniel Tosh is coming to Bloomington as part of his <em>My First Farewel
 l Tour</em> arriving this spring. Tickets go on sale Friday\, November 21
  at 10 a.m. ET.</p><p>  Daniel is widely known for hosting and creating <
 i>TOSH.0</i> on Comedy Central. The show showcased internet clips with th
 e addition of Daniel's comedic perspective and was one of the longest-run
 ning comedy series for Comedy Central.</p><p>  He can currently be heard 
 and seen hosting his video podcast\, <i>TOSH SHOW</i>. The show premiered
  garnering millions of watches and listens in the first weeks.</p><p>  Da
 niel has performed live stand-up comedy to sold out venues all over the w
 orld including New Zealand\, Australia\, Montreal\, and Ireland. Followin
 g his 2025 US <i>Daniel Tosh Live</i> tour\, he just announced his new 20
 26 North America stand-up tour\, <i>Daniel Tosh:</i><i>My First Farewell 
 Tour</i>.</p>
