SUMMARY:The STARS Tour Featuring Anne Wilson
DESCRIPTION:Join Grammy-nominated singer-songwriter Anne Wilson for the s
 econd leg of The STARS Tour presented by TPR.\, this Spring.  Come get a 
 first look at new music from her recently released album STARS\, alongsid
 e fan favorites like "Rain in the Rearview\," "Strong\," "Hey Girl\," and
  her multi-week No. 1 smash "My Jesus." Don't miss a powerful night of mu
 sic\, worship\, and a look at what's to come.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join Grammy-nominated singer-songwriter
  Anne Wilson for the second leg of The STARS Tour presented by TPR.\, thi
 s Spring.</p><p>  Come get a first look at new music from her recently re
 leased album <em>STARS</em>\, alongside fan favorites like "Rain in the R
 earview\," "Strong\," "Hey Girl\," and her multi-week No. 1 smash "My Jes
 us." Don't miss a powerful night of music\, worship\, and a look at what'
 s to come.</p>
