  astonishing set\, and a score that's out of this Netherworld\, <i>Beetle
 juice</i> is "screamingly good fun" (<i>Variety</i>). And under its uproa
 rious surface (six feet under\, to be exact)\, it's a remarkably touching
  show about family\, love\, and making the most of every Day-O!<br /><br 
 />  Recommended for ages 13+. Parental discretion advised.</p>
